WEBVTT

00:00.483 --> 00:01.917
The thing that worries me
is you girls thinking

00:02.017 --> 00:04.886
you can just change
the rules as you go along.

00:04.978 --> 00:07.601
Dee Ann, I'm afraid we're
gonna have to part ways.

00:07.602 --> 00:09.036
You're firing her?

00:09.137 --> 00:12.272
Will you just do me one favor? Stay
as far away from me as possible.

00:12.373 --> 00:13.540
We give each other
some space,

00:13.641 --> 00:15.409
and, hopefully, we won't wind up
killing each other.

00:15.510 --> 00:17.577
You want to know the fascinating
thing about power?

00:17.679 --> 00:19.880
Piss off the wrong people,
and it can change.

00:19.981 --> 00:21.348
What's that
supposed to mean?

00:21.449 --> 00:25.318
It means, from this moment on,
the clock is ticking.

00:25.420 --> 00:27.821
I hear that some of the girls
here offer more than massages.

00:27.922 --> 00:29.690
What are you looking for?
What can I get?

00:29.791 --> 00:32.292
Why don't you
spell it out for me?

00:34.028 --> 00:36.505
I know you...from the spa
down in Sugar Land.

00:36.530 --> 00:37.664
Good memory.

00:37.665 --> 00:39.166
Seeing as how you and me
are old friends,

00:39.267 --> 00:40.667
I'm gonna just let you off
with a warning.

00:40.768 --> 00:41.668
I really appreciate that.

00:41.769 --> 00:43.170
I didn't think
I'd be doing it alone.

00:43.271 --> 00:45.172
I'm so sorry
that I was mean to you.

00:45.273 --> 00:48.175
You don't need to apologize,
and you are not alone.

00:48.276 --> 00:49.309
I'm not going anywhere.

00:52.547 --> 00:53.747
Hey. You're calling late.

00:53.848 --> 00:55.716
About last night,
we should talk.

00:55.817 --> 00:57.317
We're talking right now.
In person.

00:57.418 --> 00:58.452
I'm coming over.

00:58.553 --> 01:01.421
It's late, and we'll talk.
I promise.

01:03.558 --> 01:04.757
Kyle.

01:05.860 --> 01:07.928
[ Insects chirping ]

01:11.699 --> 01:13.467
There's nothing
that I can do or say

01:13.568 --> 01:15.102
to make up
for what I've done.

01:15.203 --> 01:17.037
All right?

01:17.138 --> 01:19.005
I can't tell you how many times
I've wanted to come back,

01:19.107 --> 01:21.241
dreamed of
what I would say

01:21.342 --> 01:24.711
and how I would
make it up to you, and...

01:24.812 --> 01:26.780
Now that I'm standing here
looking at you, I just...

01:29.617 --> 01:30.617
Lord knows
you have every right

01:30.718 --> 01:31.785
to just slam the door
in my face,

01:31.886 --> 01:34.955
but I just -- wait.

01:40.695 --> 01:43.163
Can I at least peek in
and see the kids?

01:43.188 --> 01:47.188
<font color=#00FF00>♪ The Client List 1x10 ♪</font>
